  m_text: "Constance and Alice begin to struggle. The Queen\u2019s guilty verdict
    hangs in the air as the guards swarm them.\n\nThe girls desperately fight and
    try to break free but nothing helps. \n\nThey\u2019re dragged away, the look
    on the Queen\u2019s face is cold and uninterested. The court room doors slam
    shut with a final thud.\r\n"
